<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
		<title>FAQ - Partenaires</title>
		<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css"/>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css"/>
		{{ encore_entry_link_tags('landing') }}
		<style>
			.gradient-text {
				background: linear-gradient(to right, #ec008c, #f6941f);
				-webkit-background-clip: text;
				-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
				font-family: 'UrbaneRounded', sans-serif;
				font-weight: 600;
			}

			.title-gradient {
				font-family: 'UrbaneRounded', sans-serif;
				font-size: 24px;
				font-weight: 600;
				background: linear-gradient(to right, #ec008c, #f6941f);
				-webkit-background-clip: text;
				-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
			}

			.logo-container {
				width: 60px;
				height: 60px;
				border-radius: 10px;
				box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
				overflow: hidden;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
			}

			.logo-container img {
				max-width: 80%;
				max-height: 80%;
				object-fit: contain;
			}

			.btn-gradient {
				background: linear-gradient(to right, #ec008c, #f6941f);
				border: none;
				color: #fff;
				font-weight: 600;
				padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 30px;
				transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
			}

			.btn-gradient:hover {
				opacity: 0.9;
				color: #fff;
			}

			.gradient-line {
				width: 60px;
				height: 4px;
				background: linear-gradient(to right, #ec008c, #f6941f);
				margin: 0 auto;
			}

			.link-column ul {
				list-style: none;
				padding: 0;
			}

			.link-column a {
				text-decoration: none;
				color: #333;
			}

			.logo-container img {
				height: 40px;
			}

			.faq-hero {
				background: url('{{ asset('build/images/background-homepagz.png') }}') center center / cover no-repeat fixed;
				min-height: 50vh;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				text-align: center;
				padding: 2rem;
				position: relative;
				color: white;
			}

			.faq-hero::before {
				content: "";
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				z-index: 1;
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
				backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
				-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
			}

			.faq-hero h1 {
				font-size: 2rem;
				z-index: 2;
				position: relative;
			}

			@media(min-width: 768px) {
				.faq-hero h1 {
					font-size: 3rem;
				}
			}

			.faq-section {
				padding: 4rem 0;
				background-color: #fff;
			}

			.accordion-button:not(.collapsed) {
				background: linear-gradient(to right, #ec008c, #f6941f);
				color: white;
			}

			.accordion-button {
				font-weight: 600;
			}

			.accordion-item {
				border-radius: 1rem;
				overflow: hidden;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				border: 1px solid #ddd;
			}

			.link-column ul {
				list-style: none;
				padding: 0;
			}

			.link-column a {
				text-decoration: none;
				color: #333;
			}

			.logo-container img {
				height: 40px;
			}

			.title-gradient {
				font-weight: bold;
				background: linear-gradient(to right, #ec008c, #f6941f);
				-webkit-background-clip: text;
				-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
			}
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>

		{% include 'landing_page/_navbar.html.twig' %}

		<div style="margin-top: 80px;"></div>

		<section class="faq-hero">
			<h1 class="text-white">FOIRE AUX QUESTIONS</h1>
		</section>

		<section class="faq-section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="text-center mb-4 textspecial">Trouvez les réponses à vos questions</h2>
				<div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
					<div class="accordion-item" data-aos="fade-up">
						<h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq1">
							<button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse1">
								Comment activer la supervision de ma borne ?
							</button>
						</h2>
						<div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="faq1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
							<div class="accordion-body">
								Pour activer la supervision, vous devez insérer la carte SIM M2M fournie, scanner le QR code sécurisé et
								              suivre le guide de mise en supervision.
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="accordion-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
						<h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq2">
							<button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
								Le kit est-il compatible avec toutes les bornes ?
							</button>
						</h2>
						<div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
							<div class="accordion-body">
								Le kit est conçu pour fonctionner avec les bornes disposant d’un emplacement pour carte SIM. Veuillez
								              vérifier la compatibilité avec votre fabricant.
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="accordion-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
						<h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq3">
							<button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
								Que faire si la supervision ne fonctionne pas ?
							</button>
						</h2>
						<div id="collapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq3" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
							<div class="accordion-body">
								Contactez notre support technique via le formulaire de contact ou consultez la section aide pour un
								              dépannage étape par étape.
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="accordion-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
						<h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq4">
							<button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
								Quels sont les délais de livraison ?
							</button>
						</h2>
						<div id="collapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq4" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
							<div class="accordion-body">
								Les livraisons sont généralement effectuées sous 3 à 5 jours ouvrés après la validation de votre commande.
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>


		{% include 'landing_page/_footer.html.twig' %}

	 <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
		 <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
		 <script>
		    AOS.init({
		      once: true,
		      duration: 1000
		    });
		  </script>
	</body>

</html>
